{"tid":2255823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter係咪進一步自我審查？","createTime":"2020-10-24T01:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T23:00:55.000Z","uid":195944,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bac4842a4463f2c92200b47090c26b325b410371","tid":2255823,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:05:11.000Z","msg":"早兩日仲係like, retweet就得 過程一秒都唔駛<br />\n<br />\n直到前日 個過程變得複雜<br />\n<br />\nLike都係撳一次就得<br />\n<br />\n但係retweet就要先撳retweet 入咗條tweet到再撳多次retweet<br />\n<br />\n有某強國依啲字眼仲麻煩 先要撳一次轉推 佢會問你會不會先睇下篇文章先 雖然有制可以引用推文 要再撳轉推佢先retweet到 即係平時兩次 依家要三次先推到<br />\n<br />\n有無咁賤呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能會話兩次定三次差唔多 但咁講就錯喇 因為佢啲轉推制喺唔同位置 要好小心先唔會撳錯 浪費多一倍時間<br />\n<br />\n有無咁驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁定我自己問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489cc8ce98db6c9544ef9ea481bd69528f5fcb67","tid":2255823,"uid":195944,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"小白鼠先生係咪一個團隊定一個人<br />\n<br />\n每日起身睇到我暈<br />\n<br />\n我眼睛去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552d33b5f49f523381f5072f0b55ae5fc3ebb98c","tid":2255823,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:15:47.000Z","msg":"每日retweet 看盡天下事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930180b33f678a89bfc8ae4e803fc1025f3be241","tid":2255823,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:18:46.000Z","msg":"李飛飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c708fcdfc9186db6811c8aa58a39cc22f65f5c6","tid":2255823,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"930180b33f678a89bfc8ae4e803fc1025f3be241","tid":2255823,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T01:18:46.000Z","msg":"李飛飛 <img src=\"/assets/face